Package Description
com.java.GameEngine
Game Engine package provides generic classes that is a blueprint for the game design
com.java.GameEngine.Audio
Audio package is used to load and play audio files.
com.java.GameEngine.Controller
Controller package is the main logic of the Game Engine class that controls View and Model
com.java.GameEngine.log
Log package is used for logging.
com.java.GameEngine.Model
Model package is the data part of the game engine.
com.java.GameEngine.View
View class contains Display that is shown to user.
